{"id":"7a21546f-9877-4a12-8bf9-54362f26261b","name":"Disney Sorcerer's Arena RPG","description":"<p><strong><em>Disney Sorcerer's Arena</em></strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\"> was a </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://disney.fandom.com/wiki/Crossovers\" target=\"_blank\"><u>crossover</u></a><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\"> mobile role-playing game that launched globally on </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://disney.fandom.com/wiki/March_24\" target=\"_blank\"><u>March 24</u></a><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">, </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://disney.fandom.com/wiki/2020\" target=\"_blank\"><u>2020</u></a><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">. The game featured </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://disney.fandom.com/wiki/The_Walt_Disney_Company\" target=\"_blank\"><u>Disney</u></a><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\"> and </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://disney.fandom.com/wiki/Pixar\" target=\"_blank\"><u>Pixar</u></a><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\"> characters and combined RPG with card-based combat and fighting gameplay. This was the second Disney fighting game on mobile, next after </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://disney.fandom.com/wiki/Disney_Heroes:_Battle_Mode\" target=\"_blank\"><em><u>Disney Heroes: Battle Mode</u></em></a><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">.</span></p><h2><span><strong>Synopsis</strong></span></h2><p><em>Disney Sorcerer's Arena</em> combined real-time action and RPG strategy, summoning Disney and Pixar characters directly from their collectible cards into battle on an unending quest to be legendary!</p><h2><span><strong>Playable Characters</strong></span></h2><p>FranchiseCharacters<a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://disney.fandom.com/wiki/One_Hundred_and_One_Dalmatians\" target=\"_blank\"><em>101 Dalmatians</em></a><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"mw-file-description image\" href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/disney/images/c/c3/DSA_token_cruella_de_vil.png/revision/latest?cb=20230821184537\" target=\"_blank\"><span></span></a><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://disney.fandom.com/wiki/A_Bug%27s_Life\" target=\"_blank\"><em>A Bug's Life</em></a><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"mw-file-description image\" href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/disney/images/f/f1/DSA_token_hopper.png/revision/latest?cb=20230821184608\" target=\"_blank\"><span></span></a><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://disney.fandom.com/wiki/A_Goofy_Movie\" target=\"_blank\"><em>A Goofy Movie</em></a><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"mw-file-description image\" href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/disney/images/0/00/DSA_token_max_goof.png/revision/latest?cb=20230902025503\" target=\"_blank\"><span></span></a><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"mw-file-description image\" href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/disney/images/9/96/DSA_token_powerline.png/revision/latest?cb=20230902025524\" target=\"_blank\"><span></span></a><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://disney.fandom.com/wiki/Aladdin_(film)\" target=\"_blank\"><em>Aladdin</em></a><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"mw-file-description","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"RwFtnF-X6Ifd-ZexN9vVK.webp","creator":"noahspiderrocks","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","👩‍🦰 Female","🧑‍🎨 OC","🎮 Game","🦸 Hero","🔮 Magical","👭 Multiple","❤️‍🩹 Fluff"],"chats":18,"messages":468,"created_at":"2026-02-26T18:01:30.081036+00:00"}